- Clarify public docs guidance in AGENTS.md

Behavior
- Android/Chromium: shows install banner (beforeinstallprompt) + Install button; caches top page
- iOS: shows “Share → Add to Home Screen” banner; works standalone
- Offline: navigations serve cached /index.html; fallback to /offline.html

Notes
- Everything under /docs is publicly served at https://todo.moukaeritai.work/
- Bump CACHE_NAME in sw.js to invalidate old caches when changing assets